<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account | Ticketsystem</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css?v=2">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen">
    <nav class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between h-16">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 5v2m0 4v2m0 4v2M5 5a2 2 0 00-2 2v3a2 2 0 110 4v3a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-3a2 2 0 110-4V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5z"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 hover:text-primary-600">Ticketsystem</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden md:ml-8 md:flex md:space-x-1">
                        <a href="/" class="nav-link">Dashboard</a>
                        <% if (role === 'admin' || role === 'root') { %>
                        <a href="/stats" class="nav-link">Statistiken</a>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-600"><%= user %> <span class="badge bg-gray-100 text-gray-700"><%= role %></span></span>
                    <a href="/account" class="btn-secondary text-sm border-primary-200 text-primary-700">Account</a>
                    <a href="/logout" class="btn-secondary text-sm">Abmelden</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
        <div class="mb-8 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Mein Account</h1>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">Passwort und hinterlegte E-Mail-Adresse selbst verwalten.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/" class="btn-secondary text-sm">Zurück zum Dashboard</a>
        </div>

        <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="mb-6 rounded-lg border border-red-200 bg-red-50 p-4 text-sm text-red-700"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>
        <% if (success) { %>
        <div class="mb-6 rounded-lg border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 p-4 text-sm text-emerald-700"><%= success %></div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Zugangsdaten</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <% if (isRootAccount) { %>
                    <div class="rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-4 text-sm text-amber-800">
                        Das Root-Konto wird aktuell über Umgebungsvariablen verwaltet. Passwort und E-Mail können daher nicht in dieser Ansicht geändert werden.
                    </div>
                    <% } else if (!account) { %>
                    <div class="rounded-xl border border-red-200 bg-red-50 p-4 text-sm text-red-700">
                        Zu diesem Login wurde kein aktives Benutzerkonto gefunden.
                    </div>
                    <% } else { %>
                    <form method="post" action="/account" class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
                            <div>
                                <label class="mb-1 block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Benutzername</label>
                                <input value="<%= account.username %>" disabled class="form-input w-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-500">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label class="mb-1 block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Rolle</label>
                                <input value="<%= account.role %>" disabled class="form-input w-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-500">
                            </div>
                            <div class="md:col-span-2">
                                <label class="mb-1 block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">E-Mail-Adresse</label>
                                <% if (account.staff_id) { %>
                                <input name="email" type="email" value="<%= account.staff_email || '' %>" required class="form-input w-full" placeholder="name@beispiel.de">
                                <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">Die Adresse wird im verknüpften Mitarbeiterdatensatz aktualisiert.</p>
                                <% } else { %>
                                <input value="Kein Mitarbeiter verknüpft" disabled class="form-input w-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-500">
                                <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">Für diesen Benutzer ist kein Mitarbeiterprofil verknüpft, daher kann hier keine E-Mail gespeichert werden.</p>
                                <% } %>
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-5 md:col-span-2 md:max-w-md">
                                <div>
                                    <label class="mb-1 block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Neues Passwort</label>
                                    <input name="password" type="password" class="form-input w-full" placeholder="Leer lassen, wenn unverändert">
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <label class="mb-1 block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Passwort bestätigen</label>
                                    <input name="password_confirm" type="password" class="form-input w-full" placeholder="Zur Kontrolle wiederholen">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-end border-t border-slate-200 pt-5">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Account speichern</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Zuordnung</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500">Mitarbeiter</p>
                            <p class="mt-1 text-base font-medium text-slate-900"><%= account && account.staff_name ? account.staff_name : 'Nicht verknüpft' %></p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500">Hauptsystem</p>
                            <p class="mt-1 text-base font-medium text-slate-900"><%= account && account.system_name ? account.system_name : 'Nicht gesetzt' %></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Hinweis</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body text-sm text-slate-600">
                        Passwortänderungen wirken sofort beim nächsten Login. Die E-Mail-Adresse wird dort geändert, wo das System heute Benachrichtigungen für den verknüpften Mitarbeiter versendet.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>